---
title: Smokey Crumbed Pork & Apple Cos Salad with Herby-Mayo Dressing
description: Get ready for a deliciously crunchy twist on your weeknight dinner! This crumbed pork is perfectly golden, crispy, and oh-so-juicy. Paired with a fresh, crisp apple salad, this dish has the perfect balance of textures and flavours.
